snippet.title: Our Life: Beginnings & Always Kickstarter Trailer
snippet.description:
Our Life is a nostalgic Visual Novel where you create your own character and grow from childhood to adulthood with the lonely boy next door. It's currently in development by GB Patch Games. 

Patreon: https://www.patreon.com/gbpatch
Twitter: https://twitter.com/patch_games
Tumblr: https://gb-patch.tumblr.com/
Discord: https://discord.gg/Q9YvQx2
Itch.io: https://gbpatch.itch.io/our-life
Funded Kickstarter Page: https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/gbpatch/1165539954?ref=8mk0r8&token=68dcdfd7
